The following table details the expected action
and estimates for the inflation forecasts of policy board members. All 18
economists surveyed by  Bloomberg News  predict no easing at the next policy
meeting on April 26. The bank will release inflation forecasts for FY 2013,
FY 2014, and may announce forecasts for FY 2015. All inflation forecasts exclude
the effects of the sales tax increase.  To contact the reporters on this story:
